The evidence with the title 'Solar employs more people in U.S. electricity generation than oil ... ' says Jan 25, 2017  ... In the United States , more people were employed in solar power last year than in generating electricity through coal , gas and oil energy combined.  ... Fuel production and electricity generation together directly employed 1.9  ... Solar energy added 73,615 new jobs to the U.S. economy over the past year  ... 
